measurements.description: Sixteen flowers on one 83.5-cm arched inflorescence; sepals and petals yellow overlaid light maroon, veined deep maroon midline, yellow picotee; lip bright yellow spotted deep burgundy basally, midlobe blotched and diffused deep burgundy apically, burgundy midline, yellow picotee, side lobes spotted deep burgundy; column yellow suffused burgundy, striped burgundy ventrally, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
